verbose_text: Compared with the untreated control group, the increase in EPC apoptosis, as well as in Bax and caspase-3 expression was significant following treatment with 150 ng/ml visfatin, which also induced a dose dependent and significant increase in the protein expression of interleukin-6 (IL-6) and intercellular adhesion molecule-1 (ICAM-1).
evidence: expression of interleukin-6 (IL-6) and intercellular adhesion molecule-1
